{"tid":1460440,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] [上線啦!!!] 夢遊機場 Online攻略","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:30:11.000Z","uid":72510,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"86367aee3f7dc7cfc39a40d245d58c13823586c0","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"最近新出左隻Online game，想分享下玩法。 <br />\n成隻遊戲最主要既戰場係機場我諗大家都知，但點樣夢遊，同夢遊目的其實大家都有唔同睇法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下係小弟看法：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">夢遊目的：</span></span><br />\n1. 提高外國關注情度<br />\n2. 向旅客宣傳<br />\n3. 向政府施壓<br />\n<br />\nDHL員工有嘢想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459441</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對上夢遊成績：</span></span><br />\n往返航班受阻：<br />\n1. 粗略估算一天損失100億貨運量 (FROM 巴打)<br />\n2. 鄰國出口關稅上升 <br />\n3. 外媒大幅報導<br />\n4. 大量旅客滯留 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成績有目共睹！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前提：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 不送頭不受傷不分化不割蓆不指責！！！</span><br />\n2. 認清目標，目的達成後轉場／散場<br />\n3. 不定期進行遊戲，增加對家佈防準備及時間<br />\n<br />\n頭目技能不外乎<span style=\"color: red;\">擊殺</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">捕獲</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">誘敵</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">間諜</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要行流如水</span></span>，敵退我進，敵進我退，消耗對方。<br />\n切記唔好輕易讓頭目放大技清場，亦唔好心存僥倖無衝擊就無清場<br />\n頭目係會自帶衝擊技能！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">頭目戰只要一次失足，將會兵敗如山倒，再無戰友上線。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩法（日與夜）：</span></span><br />\n日（９ＡＭ &mdash;７ＰＭ）：<br />\n1. 首先要不阻任何車輛出入，令機場玩家<span style=\"color: red;\">人數累積</span>，有人數有旅客大家先會安全<br />\n2. 累積相當人數後定期收集數據同消息，密切<span style=\"color: red;\">注意機場風向</span><br />\n3. 與此同時，行車道要開始有出無入，<span style=\"color: red;\">增加頭目佈防難度</span>，提高玩家存活率<br />\n4. 風向一變，目的達成，支援型玩家請<span style=\"color: red;\">分批撤離，保持流通性</span>，提高存活率<br />\n5. 進攻型玩家可按情況留守或殿後，儘量<span style=\"color: red;\">保存戰力及拖延頭目回復時間</span><br />\n<br />\n夜 （１０ＰＭ &mdash;５ＡＭ 貨運主要戰場 From 巴打）：<br />\n我諗大家都知遊戲地圖參照香港機場，所以小弟我搵左3個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">短距離無限輪迴位</span></span>，作駕駛初哥練習，迴旋處唔出就話有可能比GM 封AC姐，依家我彈出彈入你咬我食呀？<br />\n<br />\n路線如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPGcQM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPGcQM6.png&h=7fdd53c4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上圖係客運主要道路，你懂的！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcrkfdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcrkfdR.jpg&h=4bc04afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貨運主要道路，星位標示為貨運出口，你懂的！<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YHxO8yV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYHxO8yV.jpg&h=e8f695e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一貨運出口支線，你懂的！<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1. 玩家請帶備備用衣物一套（咩色都OK）及旅行裝備，離開時作偽裝<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">自組禁區防線</span>，長期拍攝，以防間諜自帶衝擊技能<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">穿著黑色衣物</span>，易分自己人，街衫好易比間諜滲入<br />\n4. 玩家請自發組隊及<span style=\"color: red;\">自發關閉電話</span>（如非必要情況），每隊只開一部電話，以減少網絡負擔<br />\n5. 哨兵，情報員<span style=\"color: red;\">請fact check</span><br />\n<br />\n好撚認真咁教你地做一次fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n6. 不定期遊玩&lt;-好重要，唔好日日玩<br />\n<br />\n最後祝遊玩愉快"},{"pid":"091d0c76e7e34862eb49c94dbce882be093b92a8","tid":1460440,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"推番機場POST出黎"},{"pid":"5ff3cefb2686e27729d3cfb9e6766aaaa2011cd1","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1b6ee8ebfc3d6e638ffca9b075dc78797d9c4f4","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"歡迎各路攻略提供"},{"pid":"8de1bc60d556470ffdb7993335d826ae334851c9","tid":1460440,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"推番機場主POST出黎  今日冇哂聲氣  士氣!!"},{"pid":"19b69b538fd296778d176fabda230e21150e8113","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1085d0fed87fb9afd358b25d778db9a22815d7e1","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"104a51c9ad62103d61c8a4f2fa692bd22f0dd060","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58365cf18f1ab798b7ff7a0b71f0db59a83b1d3c","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68751cc9c72de0701c6abfbc5446b4e3ea03130e","tid":1460440,"uid":270148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"一定要推！！！今日下晝見！！！等睇林鄭條仆街日撚日出黎扮喊"},{"pid":"d466cf5550c307d9dd8f8460a2ca0a96a87d7758","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6df82b13822051a2c550ade3109d45b4c17b2f8","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad7764907c432dd89c8862557c192e3af9131fb","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"048568ec3092ead10b646290b4b1b08f3220bbf6","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid