dBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"屌一兩句就話人分化。事實係乜野阿，事實係依家機場好撚多人阿<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZvpHZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZvpHZA.jpg&h=00aecb20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d20aa2fb06c59960fd706f01311ab80c9c3f95d","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46b05ebc10e239a49ae11f8e2ac1e6cb80e7b435","tid":1460440,"uid":306061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d86ca79ec706e175848e06e8bae85fa69ceb582","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"534b1a7e0e99ce159e161ff645bf578ced9ee72a","tid":1460440,"uid":39287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">散水撚好波</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"依個時候仲分化，係人係鬼等大家分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"屌一兩句就話人分化。事實係乜野阿，事實係依家機場好撚多人阿<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZvpHZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZvpHZA.jpg&h=00aecb20&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"巴打，請問你句事實好多人用意何在？<br />\n屌手足有咩意思？只會令更多和理非灰心<br />\n我已經盡力同人講入一日係唔夠，係持久戰，要keep住入機場<br />\n請放眼重點，減少罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c97063888512345f23e4a64b2b2097000170e8","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"另外，各位巴請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想一支竹打一船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758564e18b340b602fc0474d00ee7b9400f39a0a","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"小弟我出Ｐｏｓｔ唔多<br />\n但總會有某幾個會員會出黎分化<br />\n某幾個會員仲會出現係其他行動Ｐｏｓｔ<br />\n帶風向都唔洗咁揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多次，我地不割不分化不指責不篤灰<br />\n做唔到不割蓆不分化不指責不篤灰，點做手足？"},{"pid":"17eb3545860c7e900bc728a6963c37076a63b144","tid":1460440,"uid":2299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:50:22.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化不指責不篤灰"},{"pid":"c14b5366f0d7d175ea90e0b8f3811b4aa0f146fb","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17eb3545860c7e900bc728a6963c37076a63b144","tid":1460440,"uid":2299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:50:22.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化不指責不篤灰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"不割蓆不分化不指責不篤灰<br />\n７１２　８１１"},{"pid":"f0945241d66eb11b86f6195e65eb29b135b9ea7e","tid":1460440,"uid":270778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"和理非 和你飛<br />\n點解你要去搞個邊交通？<br />\n點解你要搞亂和理非嘅活動？<br />\n你要連唯一一個可以和平理性嘅集會都搞砸？<br />\n人地個個辛苦嗌幾粒鐘口號，都係分享香港依家發生咩事比旅客，邊個話和理非係去癱瘓機場？<br />\n你咩心態？ 唔該用腦諗下，咪9唔搭8都諗d野出黎搞亂！你咁樣會害埋其他人！<br />\n<br />\n黑警都識假扮示威者，係哩度更加多，咪以為講句不割席就會變自己人，哩d人，割硬！"},{"pid":"412b272f9fab5ad2d0b76cc14caf80913f42caae","tid":1460440,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0945241d66eb11b86f6195e65eb29b135b9ea7e","tid":1460440,"uid":270778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"和理非 和你飛<br />\n點解你要去搞個邊交通？<br />\n點解你要搞亂和理非嘅活動？<br />\n你要連唯一一個可以和平理性嘅集會都搞砸？<br />\n人地個個辛苦嗌幾粒鐘口號，都係分享香港依家發生咩事比旅客，邊個話和理非係去癱瘓機場？<br />\n你咩心態？ 唔該用腦諗下，咪9唔搭8都諗d野出黎搞亂！你咁樣會害埋其他人！<br />\n<br />\n黑警都識假扮示威者，係哩度更加多，咪以為講句不割席就會變自己人，哩d人，割硬！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"巴打講得冇錯呀<br />\n人多車多自然會搞亂交通，唔洗主動搞<br />\n最緊要有路走，機場困獸鬥，最緊要有得走<br />\n你要鬧我，冇問題，但我講多次，狗車入唔到，大家先會更安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔推唔緊要，比多個機會我推比更多巴絲睇到就得"},{"pid":"6cbd188fdd94cbcb0f3e8a9a0a2d3fa6523f7f2a","tid":1460440,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69505bab3ac122a7da4c5b0a1445c092e0d7ba0","tid":1460440,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"Assemble<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}